---
const socials = [
  { label: 'WhatsApp', href: '#' },
  { label: 'Instagram', href: '#' },
  { label: 'YouTube', href: '#' },
  { label: 'Facebook', href: '#' },
];
---

<section class="px-5 pb-24" aria-label="Terhubung dengan kami">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div
      class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[36px] bg-gradient-to-br from-forest to-forest-dark px-8 py-16 text-center text-white sm:px-16"
      data-reveal
    >
      <div class="animate-float-slow absolute -top-16 -left-16 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="animate-float-slower absolute -bottom-20 -right-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-sky/25 blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <span class="relative inline-block rounded-full bg-white/15 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        Mari Tumbuh Bersama
      </span>
      <h2 class="relative mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-extrabold sm:text-4xl">
        Jadilah Bagian dari Satu Keluarga Besar
      </h2>
      <p class="relative mx-auto mt-3 max-w-lg text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-white/85">
        Ikuti langkah dan kegiatan kami, atau sapa kami langsung lewat media sosial —
        setiap sapaan adalah langkah menuju dunia yang lebih harmonis.
      </p>

      <div class="relative mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        {socials.map((s) => (
          <a
            href={s.href}
            data-magnetic
            class="rounded-full bg-white/15 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold backdrop-blur-sm transition-colors hover:bg-white/25"
          >
            {s.label}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
